## 🤝 Contributing

This skill is meant to be a **community project**. Contributions are very welcome!

### How to Contribute
1. Fork this repository
2. Make your changes (improve analysis rules, add new sections, update data sources, fix wording, etc.)
3. Open a Pull Request with a clear description of what you changed and why
4. I'll review and merge good contributions 
5. Or Fork and make it Better I'm sure to use yours if its better !!


**All contributions may be  credited** in the skill description and README.

